column5: I saw 2 of them on the side of the 401 coming back from Quinte.
As long as ya tell everyone inside to plug their ears............Shoot away!
Wouldn't be the first time the gun discharged from that patio door Andy!!
Wayne  they'll ruin a garden faster than anything. I have a very quiet crossbow and will be willing to help you out.  Would hate to see good money spent on flowers get eaten.
We saw a hen and Tom north of Dorset (HWY 60) Sunday afternoon, that is the furthest North we have seen them so far.
